quran[25{c,v,t}:
26,112,"Nooh ne kaha"" mein kya jaanun ke un ke amal kaisay hain"
26,113,"un ka hisaab to mere rab ke zimma hai, kash tum kuch shaoor se kaam lau"
26,114,mera yeh kaam nahi hai ke jo imaan layein un ko mein dhtkar dun
26,115,"mein to bas aik saaf saaf mutnabba kar dainay wala aadmi hon """
26,116,"unhon ne kaha"" ae Nooh, agar to baz nah aaya tu phatkary hu-ay logon mein shaamil ho kar rahay ga """
26,117,"Nooh ne dua ki"" “aymere rab, meri qoum ne mujhe jhutla diya"
26,118,"ab mere aur un ke darmain do toak faisla kar day aur mujhe aur jo momin mere sath hain un ko nijaat day """
26,119,aakhir kaar hum ne is ko aur is ke sathiyon ko aik bhari hui kashti mein bacha liya
26,120,aur is ke baad baqi logon ko ghark kar diya
26,121,"yaqeenan is mein aik nishani hai, magar un mein se aksar log maan-ne walay nahi"
26,122,aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke tera rab zabardast bhi hai aur Raheem bhi
26,123,Aad ne Rasolo-n ko jhatlaya
26,124,"yaad karo jabkay un ke bhai hood ne un se kaha tha"" kya tum drtay nahi ?"
26,125,mein tumahray liye aik amanat daar rasool hon
26,126,lehaza tum Allah se daro aur meri itaat karo
26,127,mein is kaam par tum se kisi ajar ka taalib nahi hon mera ajar to rab alameen ke zimma hai
26,128,yeh tumhara kya haal hai ke har ounchay maqam par laa haasil aik yadgar imarat bana daaltay ho
26,129,aur barray barray qasr taamer karte ho goya tumhe hamesha rehna hai
26,130,aur jab kisi par haath daaltay ho jabbar ban kar daaltay ho
26,131,pas tum log Allah se daro aur meri itaat karo
26,132,daro uss se jis ne woh kuch tumhe diya hai jo tum jantay ho
26,133,"tumhe janwar diye, avladin den"
26,134,baagh diye aur chashmay diye
26,135,"mujhe tumahray haq mein aik barray din ke azaab ka dar hai """
26,136,"unhon ne jawab diya"" to nasiyaat kar ya nah kar, hamaray liye yaksaa hai"
